The national leader of the All Progressives Congress, Bola Tinubu, on Thursday visited Ibrahim Badamasi Babangida (IBB), former military Head of State at his Minna residence, Niger State.Tinubu arrived at the hilltop residence of the retired General at about 2.30pm and both went straight into a meeting behind closed doors. File photo used to illustrate story.



